    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Simply put, this AstraZeneca paper misses the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elephant_in_the_room" target="_self">elephant in the room</a>. This problem is still not addressed in more recent papers by other AstraZeneca researchers (<a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1704.07555" target="_self">here</a> and <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1711.07839" target="_self">here</a>).</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
